summary: Utility module that provides helper functions for converting and handling tensors during TensorRT LLM export, including fetching tensors from dictionaries, accessing tensor parallel groups, splitting tensors for model parallelism, and converting PyTorch tensors to NumPy arrays with specific data types.
business_intent: Enable seamless transformation and management of tensors when exporting large language models to TensorRT, ensuring correct data types, parallel group handling, and tensor partitioning for efficient inference.
